| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3844 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7283e584-c8f0-55d7-80a3-6b7bc789ec5a"
